const siteData={
    siteImage:"https://www.doodleblue.com/images/home/client-testimonial-quotes.jpg",
    para:"What clients have to say about us"
}

const mockData=[
{
    id:1,
  Image :"https://www.doodleblue.com/images/home/clienttestimonial/validus.png;",
  quoteIcon:"https://www.doodleblue.com/images/home/client-quote.png",
  para:"We were amazed by doodleblue's “let us try another approach” attitude, which has helped us with every hurdle of our complex project. They always have an alternate solution to issues and never dying spirit.",
  name:"Sauvik D",
  title:"Founding team,validus"
},
{
    id:2,
Image: "https://www.doodleblue.com/images/home/clienttestimonial/mobily.png;",
quoteIcon:"https://www.doodleblue.com/images/home/client-quote.png",
para: "We appreciate doodleblue’s all-time availability and cooperation. They are extremely responsive and provide excellent client servicing.",
name:"Mohammed A alijalal",
title:"Director digital channels,mobility"
},
{
    id:3,
Image:"https://www.doodleblue.com/images/home/clienttestimonial/star.png;",
quoteIcon:"https://www.doodleblue.com/images/home/client-quote.png",
para:"We developed a great partnership with doodleblue. Their dedication to work is evident in every aspect of the app. We appreciate their attention to details and their creative approach.",
name:"Senthil",
title:"CIO ,Star Health"
},
{
    id:4,
Image:"https://www.doodleblue.com/images/home/clienttestimonial/bijilipay.png",
quoteIcon:"https://www.doodleblue.com/images/home/client-quote.png",
para:"doodleblue’s cooperation and empathetic nature has helped us build the product of our dreams with ease.",
name:"Eniyan Narayanaswamy",
title:"Chief Product Officer,BijliPay"
},
{
    id:5,
Image :"https://www.doodleblue.com/images/home/clienttestimonial/sarva.png",
quoteIcon:"https://www.doodleblue.com/images/home/client-quote.png",
para:"We were actively looking for a CTO to hire into the system and figure out our entire digital transformation. I must tell you that I am not sure about even if I had a full-time CTO, I would have had somebody like doodleblue.",
name:"Sarvesh Sashi",
title:"Founder and CEO,Sarva"
},
{
    id:6,
Image:"https://www.doodleblue.com/images/home/clienttestimonial/wildwarrior.png",
quoteIcon:"https://www.doodleblue.com/images/home/client-quote.png",
para:"I had, of course, heard about doodleblue and decided to try them out on a critical project that involved transforming our user experience and going deep into the engineering to resolve technical nuances. It was a pleasure to work with them!",
name:"Somdev Devvarman",
title:"International Tennis Champion"
},
{
    id:7,
Image:"https://www.doodleblue.com/images/home/clienttestimonial/addz.png",
quoteIcon:"https://www.doodleblue.com/images/home/client-quote.png",
para:"We had started our project with another developer and after about a year and a half of frustration we moved all development to doodleblue. We couldn't be more happy with our decision and consider doodleblue as a trusted advisor and partner in our journey.",
name:"Adam Ruetz",
title:"Co-Founder,ODDZ app"
},
{
    id:8,
Image:"https://www.doodleblue.com/images/home/clienttestimonial/flyy.png",
quoteIcon:"https://www.doodleblue.com/images/home/client-quote.png",
para:"doodleblue's technical strength is their biggest plus point. Our experience with them has been very positive. We’re looking to engage them in other projects as well.",
name:"Yasar Arafath",
title:"Head of Software division"
},
{
    id:9,
Image:"https://www.doodleblue.com/images/home/clienttestimonial/kluo.png",
quoteIcon:"https://www.doodleblue.com/images/home/client-quote.png",
para:"We were looking for a company to see our vision, understand our target market and deliver on time. To get the best of both worlds is fairly hard to get and we were able to pick this up with doodleblue, so we are delighted.",
name:"Tyler Sellers",
title:"CEO of kluo app"
},
{
    id:10,
Image:"https://www.doodleblue.com/images/home/clienttestimonial/eshakti.png",
quoteIcon:"https://www.doodleblue.com/images/home/client-quote.png",
para:"Simply put dedication to work, client-centric engagement, high-quality delivery, desire to deliver beyond the promise, concenience of engagement are some of the traitsone will come accross when partnering with doodleblue",
name:"Varun L",
title:"Product Manager eSakthi"
},
{
    id:11,
Image:"https://www.doodleblue.com/images/home/clienttestimonial/beezergolf.png",
quoteIcon:"https://www.doodleblue.com/images/home/client-quote.png",
para:"The doodleblue team helped us build the best golf game app in the market. The app has a very comprehensive golf scorecard . Its UI is a step ahead of the competition. The doodleblue development team had get iOS development and UX expertise",
name:"Anotonio Casacuberta",
title:"Founder Beezer Golf LLC"
},
{
    id:12,
Image:"https://www.doodleblue.com/images/home/clienttestimonial/crayon.png",
quoteIcon:"https://www.doodleblue.com/images/home/client-quote.png",
para:"We have been quite impressed with the skill level and flexibility they offered us. doodleblue has always helped us work towards best solutions. The deliver on time with highest standards and quality.",
name:"Priyanshu Mishra",
title:"Crayon Data"
},
]
export {siteData,mockData} ;
